{"tid":194121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人做人好無目標，無咩野追求","createTime":"2017-04-09T18:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T19:59:11.000Z","uid":2880,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e14d78d7777eb0e46d6b6efc453a60092fdb69d","tid":194121,"uid":2880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:12:09.000Z","msg":"俾人話廢青都係咁話<br />\n<br />\n無追求，唔想返工<br />\n<br />\n返工只係為食飯<br />\n<br />\n無女亦無溝女噶想法<br />\n<br />\n興趣只係睇下劇消磨時間<br />\n<br />\n無夢想，唔敢有咩夢想<br />\n<br />\n有時睇完d劇總會覺得好失落<br />\n<br />\n究竟我存在意義係咩<br />\n<br />\n雖然係劇點解我唔可以好似劇入面d人咁活得有意義<br />\n<br />\n究竟生存為乜<br />\n<br />\n同時又覺得自殺好無謂<br />\n<br />\n亦不想自殺<br />\n<br />\n渾渾噩噩<br />\n<br />\n一事無成<br />\n<br />\n有無人一樣<br />\n<br />\n有無人有共鳴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb0b5b3a65b3b91b4f498f74d0b7b7d1de239fb","tid":194121,"uid":2880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"86eb867d5d307f44a8ee46b186d9cd1aaa3fc6e7","tid":194121,"uid":70088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:15:55.000Z","msg":"明"},{"pid":"30e39fa99a75e678eace19c1e039146e04d2ac09","tid":194121,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:22:01.000Z","msg":"細個成日都會諗，大個要做啲嘢特別嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係唔知幾時開始，發覺入大學好緊要，開始放低咗興趣，玩樂，埋頭書本入面<br />\n<br />\n到頭來發覺愈嚟愈迷失，自己就愈嚟愈平凡。<br />\n<br />\n就算今日嘅自己好想拒絕呢種麻目嘅生活，但係好似已經唔記自己最想要嘅係點，或者點樣去過返開心嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n唉 我受夠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f73fe3436123fbba86ddb9194bdf136181c4407","tid":194121,"uid":71576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"人生本來就冇乜意義 日日鳩hea<br />\n有時睇見身邊啲富二代<br />\n再睇下自己...<br />\n輸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec5cde1e253bb8e02fe2f0b9429c9642e1d02b3","tid":194121,"uid":2880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個成日都會諗，大個要做啲嘢特別嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係唔知幾時開始，發覺入大學好緊要，開始放低咗興趣，玩樂，埋頭書本入面<br />\n<br />\n到頭來發覺愈嚟愈迷失，自己就愈嚟愈平凡。<br />\n<br />\n就算今日嘅自己好想拒絕呢種麻目嘅生活，但係好似已經唔記自己最想要嘅係點，或者點樣去過返開心嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n唉 我受夠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想改變又無方法改變"},{"pid":"598d55d36639d4f6bbacb0c78152e4af2484d07a","tid":194121,"uid":5990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:32:27.000Z","msg":"我唔知自己想要啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人哋尚且會為揀興趣定錢途掙扎 但我連興趣都冇 我既生活就係日日返學鳩hea 課餘上連登 唔識運動唔識打機唔識音樂唔識藝術"},{"pid":"b8be084bd98aefa85dd1598178e2bd74c391f0f5","tid":194121,"uid":2880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔知自己想要啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人哋尚且會為揀興趣定錢途掙扎 但我連興趣都冇 我既生活就係日日返學鳩hea 課餘上連登 唔識運動唔識打機唔識音樂唔識藝術</blockquote><br />\n我連打機都開始覺得悶，無人一齊玩根本唔想玩"},{"pid":"a04d866bd94d16f6a9ce408c3a7e8fb085643fdc","tid":194121,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"i want to feel alive<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ab7ec21994c633fd6b444759383ae8f972f29b","tid":194121,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾人話廢青都係咁話<br />\n<br />\n無追求，唔想返工<br />\n<br />\n返工只係為食飯<br />\n<br />\n無女亦無溝女噶想法<br />\n<br />\n興趣只係睇下劇消磨時間<br />\n<br />\n無夢想，唔敢有咩夢想<br />\n<br />\n有時睇完d劇總會覺得好失落<br />\n<br />\n究竟我存在意義係咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然係劇點解我唔可以好似劇入面d人咁活得有意義</span><br />\n<br />\n究竟生存為乜<br />\n<br />\n同時又覺得自殺好無謂<br />\n<br />\n亦不想自殺<br />\n<br />\n渾渾噩噩<br />\n<br />\n一事無成<br />\n<br />\n有無人一樣<br />\n<br />\n有無人有共鳴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得只要有夢想<br />\n就會活得有意義<br />\n不過夢想唔係發夢<br />\n係要實行"},{"pid":"63545abb5b0713e87ddd0a184d51141644249a2e","tid":194121,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:40:48.000Z","msg":"靠物慾麻目自己<br />\n打j 打機 上網 食野 <br />\n缺乏思考<br />\n其實我想上進 但又停步不前<br />\n我想感受活著既感覺<br />\n就算感受唔到 做個有意義既人都好<br />\n但又怕壓力 怕失敗 怕責任 <br />\n屌"},{"pid":"4c3ed233a4f19661da9c68cde59ab79846265d60","tid":194121,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾人話廢青都係咁話<br />\n<br />\n無追求，唔想返工<br />\n<br />\n返工只係為食飯<br />\n<br />\n無女亦無溝女噶想法<br />\n<br />\n興趣只係睇下劇消磨時間<br />\n<br />\n無夢想，唔敢有咩夢想<br />\n<br />\n有時睇完d劇總會覺得好失落<br />\n<br />\n究竟我存在意義係咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然係劇點解我唔可以好似劇入面d人咁活得有意義</span><br />\n<br />\n究竟生存為乜<br />\n<br />\n同時又覺得自殺好無謂<br />\n<br />\n亦不想自殺<br />\n<br />\n渾渾噩噩<br />\n<br />\n一事無成<br />\n<br />\n有無人一樣<br />\n<br />\n有無人有共鳴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得只要有夢想<br />\n就會活得有意義<br />\n不過夢想唔係發夢<br />\n係要實行</blockquote><br />\n咁夢想又係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個好似有好多夢想，但係通通都唔記得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c35d7353b60f9f87f142ebf81450aed58443ae2","tid":194121,"uid":16808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:41:47.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f49f9e12a62695c33b566d45f7ee4e1035a364f","tid":194121,"uid":101433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"